DESCRIPTION

Our mission is to provide the technology behind the scenes.

Our focus is to make life simpler for Clubs, labels, Booking Agencies and DJs.

We provide financial services and support to empower unsigned DJs and Businesses. Clubio is an online DJ booking platform, which allows you to book hundreds of DJs from your computer or mobile device in a matter of minutes.

Do it 8times faster with tools available to you now. You can follow your favourite DJs, share them with your crowd, check out other clubs, labels and events. User experience matters to us because it means something to our global community.
